Package: slicer
Title: Sliced Wasserstein Distances and Kernels
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan", "Vanhove", , "janvanhove@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4607-4836"))
Description: Functions for computing Wasserstein and sliced Wasserstein distances
    between empirical distributions as well as kernels derived from them. 
    Includes functions for fitting Gaussian processes using these kernels.
